---
description: No IDE or AI tool branding in git metadata or GitHub UI text
alwaysApply: true
---

# Commits and pull requests

Do not add phrases such as "Made with Cursor", "Generated with Claude", or similar IDE/AI product attribution to:

- Pull request titles or descriptions
- Commit messages
- Issue or discussion bodies you draft for the user

Write human, project-focused summaries instead (what changed and why).
